response.overview: Setlist:  01. Even If It Kills Me  02. Blood Brothers  03. Dead Cell  04. ...To Be Loved  05. Kill the Noise  06. Getting Away With Murder  07. California Love (2Pac cover) (Instrumental, with band introductions)  08. Liar  09. Forever / In the End / Changes (Linkin Park and Black Sabbath Covers; Changes sung by Jacoby acapella)  10. Leave a Light On (Talk Away the Dark) (Followed by a moment of silence)  11. Scars  12. Drum Solo  13. Braindead  14. Help  15. Born for Greatness  16. Between Angels and Insects (Bass solo outro)  17. Infest  18. Blind / My Own Summer (Shove It) / Break Stuff / Chop Suey (Korn, Deftones, Limp Bizkit and System Of a Down Covers)  19. Last Resort
response.title: Papa Roach - Live at Wacken Open Air 2025
